        "title": "Getting Started with <b>Pure Slide</b>",
        "lead": "Enjoy a keyboard ready slideshow",
        "body": [
            "with content strictly separated from markup and code.",
            "<b>Pure Slide</b> is for you,",
            "if you like to have it",
            "<br>",
            "<ul>",
            "<li>load your content from JSON</li>",
            "<li>configured easily</li>",
            "<li>arrowkey navigated</li>",
            "<li>compliant with <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"external\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vim_(text_editor)\">vim</a></li>",
            "</ul>",
            "It's built with",
            "<ul>",
            "<li><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"external\" href=\"https://bulma.io/\">Bulma CSS Framework</a></li>",
            "<li>Vanilla JS</li>",
            "</ul>"
        ],
        "next": {
            "label": "I'm excited",
            "classes": ["awesome", "grin-stars"]
        }
    },
    {
        "title": "Integrate in your site",
        "lead": "Simply provide a URL to your JSON file",
        "body": [
            "and load the pure-slide.js in your HTML header.",
            "<br><br>",
            "<div class=\"box\"><pre>",
            "&lt;script",
            "    src=\"/static/js/pure-slide.js",
            "    type=\"text/javascript\" async\"&gt;",
            "&lt;/script&gt;",
            "&lt;script&gt;",
            "    var pureSlideContentURL = 'https://url.to/your/content.json';",
            "&lt;/script&gt;",
            "</pre></div>"
        ],
        "next": {
            "label": "Dat easy"
        }
    },
    {
        "title": "Prepare your own content",
        "lead": "Just make a suitable JSON file available online",
        "body": [
            "and thus easily separate your content from the markup and code.",
            "The JSON consists of an array of one object for each card.",
            "As simple as that:",
            "<br><br>",
            "<div class=\"box\"><pre>",
            "[",
            "    { ... },",
            "    {",
            "        \"title\":  \"Prepare your own content\",",
            "        \"lead\":   \"Simply provide a URL ...\",",
            "        \"body\": [ \"and easily separate ...\",",
            "                  \"The JSON consists of ...\" ],",
            "        \"next\": { \"label\": \"Dope\"",
            "                  \"classes\": [\"awesome\", \"cannabis\"] }",
            "    }",
            "]",
            "</pre></div>"
        ],
        "next": {
            "label": "Dope",
            "classes": ["awesome", "cannabis"]
        }
    }
